<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .appointment-details {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #FEDC00;
      color: #010101;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Appointment Reminder</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

    <p>This is a reminder about your upcoming appointment:</p>

    <div class="appointment-details">
      <p><strong>Type:</strong> {{type}}</p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
      <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</p>
      {{#if isOnline}}
        <p><strong>Meeting Link:</strong> <a href="{{meetingLink}}">Join Meeting</a></p>
      {{else}}
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    {{#if isOnline}}
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{meetingLink}}" class="button">Join Meeting</a>
      </p>
    {{/if}}

    <p>If you need to reschedule or have any questions, please contact us:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: support@zoomcreatives.jp</li>
      <li>Phone: 03-6764-5723</li>
      <li>Mobile: 090-6494-5723</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>© {{year}} Zoom Creatives. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        〒130-0012 東京都墨田区太平1-11-7 グランドステータスKIYA2F<br>
        Tokyo-To, Sumida-Ku, Taihei 1-11-7 Grand Status KIYA 2F, 130-0012
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>